FBIS4-65477 "drweu095_p_94006" FBIS-WEU-94-095 Daily Report 14 May 1994 GREECE Bomb Destroys Environment Ministry Car Bomb Destroys Environment Ministry Car NC1405061594 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 0400 GMT 14 May 94 NC1405061594 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] A homemade device exploded at 2330 yesterday under a car belonging to the Environment, Town Planning, and Public Works Ministry. The car was parked on the corner of Ippokratis and Fanariotis streets and was destroyed completely. The organization, Furious Rebellion, claimed responsibility for the explosion in a phone call to the private television station, SKY.
